entist\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-ReferenceA-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-ReferenceA_3-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Cohen (1998).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/chemistry/laureates/\">\"All Nobel Prizes in Chemistry\"</a>. Nobelprize.org<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2012-06-01</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=All+Nobel+Prizes+in+Chemistry&amp;rft.pub=Nobelprize.org&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fnobelprize.org%2Fnobel_prizes%2Fchemistry%2Flaureates%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AIndependent+scientist\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Dance, Amber (2017-03-30). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v543/n7647/full/nj7647-747a.html\">\"Flexible working: Solo scientist\"</a>. <i>Nature</i>. <b>543</b> (7647): 747\u2013749. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1038/nj7647-747a\">10.1038/nj7647-747a</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Nature&amp;rft.atitle=Flexible+working%3A+Solo+scientist&amp;rft.volume=543&amp;rft.issue=7647&amp;rft.pages=747-749&amp;rft.date=2017-03-30&amp;rft_id=info%